  '<p>One primitive — <code>b.i18n</code> — covers translation lookup, locale negotiation, plural rules, formatters for date / time / number / currency, and right-to-left detection. The framework adds a request middleware that puts <code>req.locale</code>, <code>req.dir</code>, and <code>req.t</code> on every request without app code touching it.</p>',

